<item>
            <title>[LU-6180] Fix page cache flushing when group lock is cancelled</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6180</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a group lock is cancelled, it does not drop page cache entries on the client.  This has the possibility of causing memory corruption if a file is using both a group lock and regular extent lock to do IO.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="28462">LU-6180</key>
            <summary>Fix page cache flushing when group lock is cancelled</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
